{"tid":2235570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛行服務隊所以為惡係因為有香港人支持其暴行","createTime":"2020-10-08T19:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T18:55:39.000Z","uid":26770,"like":39,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fa02d68f9f3b7c1584bdb83ff619d9f28555fc3c","tid":2235570,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T19:43:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">第53頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2234901/page/53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2234901/page/53</a></span><br />\n<br />\n#1304<br />\n我終於註冊到啦<br />\n<br />\n8 小時前<br />\n啲crew 根本就唔會知個行動做啲咩！ <strong>咁樣入佢哋數，有冇搞錯！</strong><br />\n佢哋冒着生命危險救人嘅時候，又唔見你哋會搵啲班crew出嚟,佢哋救嗰啲都係人命！<br />\n再講就係佢哋乜都冇做過只係喺上空監察，<strong>監察咁又點？<br />\n而家又唔係班crew拉佢哋</strong>！佢哋同平時啲記者喺街邊直播有咩分別！<br />\n-------<br />\n#1306<br />\n甜瓜安東尼<br />\n&bull;<br />\n8 小時前<br />\n其實<strong>公開機上人員名單意義係邊</strong><br />\n咩都問唔到拿返炸沙<br />\n<br />\n呢班人真係知道<strong>自己執行咩任務</strong>？<strong>就算知</strong><br />\n<strong>你想佢地直接撞山都唔跟任務做？</strong><br />\n你都識講係驚方主導<br />\n邊個sayno邊個就有機會秋後算賬，唔做何來咁多人爆料比你<br />\n<br />\n嬲還嬲，唔好比情緒主導理性<br />\n唔係話之峰唔做嘢"},{"pid":"68bd9e8994ef0e1af8d4f2b75a7984fca0ce07e9","tid":2235570,"uid":88743,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話飛機上好有機會有警員同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bc0a0e73e1ea3aed653e42f0c6587952f9ff5f","tid":2235570,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T19:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"small\">從來無人可以一步登天</span>"},{"pid":"906d2523606029b78db477bc0db54bfd5b90f1bf","tid":2235570,"uid":88743,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"同樣既論述可以用返落白警度<br />\n太好了，考白警又可個理由了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1403c2ae0ff8abf450ffba513b3a25ff5d67f7","tid":2235570,"uid":26770,"like"